    "To counterbalance the order of grammaticality, for each phenomenon (such as Pairwise Syntactic Phenomenon 1 in Table 1), the grammatical sentence appeared above its less grammatical counterpart in four vertical pairs.",
    "Conversely, in the other four pairs, the less grammatical sentence was positioned above its grammatical mate.",
    "In total, Experiment 3 comprised 1184 trials, with an example of a trial presented as follows.",
